notes.label: Abstract

subnotes.content: Collections are stored offsite, and a minimum of 24 hours is needed to retrieve these items for use. Researchers interested in consulting any of the collections are advised to contact Special Collections.
The copyright interests in this collection remain with the creator. For more information, contact the Special Collections Library.
[Identification of Item], Records and Memorabilia regarding Student Organizations and Activities, AR.0017. University of Tennessee Libraries, Knoxville, Special Collections.
This collection is property of the University of Tennessee Archives.
This collection houses a variety of materials documenting student activities and organizations at the University of Tennessee between 1838 and 1991.
This collection consists of twelve boxes divided into four series:

items: Series I: Records and Memorabilia regarding Student Organizations and Activities, 1838-1945
Series II: Records and Memorabilia regarding Student Organizations and Activities, 1946-1959
Series II: Records and Memorabilia regarding Student Organizations and Activities, 1960-1970
Series V:  Records and Memorabilia regarding Student Organizations and Activities, 1986-1991
Series IV: Records and Memorabilia regarding Student Organizations and Activities, 1971-1985
